Not because of my rather unusual name, or because I had come from a private school.
I had only been harassed for one reason - a reason which seemed so narrow and cruel in this alleged cradle of enlightenment: My now deceased father Woodrow Wyatt was an important adviser to Margaret Thatchers and I advocated the Conservative Party.
Why am I mentioning this right now?
